OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783694874
OL,3,CWater safety campaign warns of the
OL,4,Cdangers of the Thames
OL,6,FThe Port of London Authority has
OL,7,Flaunched a new campaign on water
OL,8,Fsafety following growing concern
OL,9,Fduring the hot weather.
OL,11,FThe campaign "See the River, See the
OL,12,FRisk" follows reports that more than
OL,13,F20 people have died in the UK after
OL,14,Fgetting into difficulty in water
OL,15,Fduring the recent heatwaves.
OL,17,FThe heat and school holidays are
OL,18,Fexpected to draw more families and
OL,19,Fteenagers to London's waterways.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
