CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783694874
OL,3,CWater safety campaign warns of the
OL,4,Cdangers of the Thames
OL,6,FIt is a new campaign aimed at 10-16
OL,7,Fyear olds across London, Kent and
OL,8,FEssex.
OL,10,FIt warns that young Londoners
OL,11,Funderestimate the risks of the tidal
OL,12,FThames.
OL,14,FThe Port of London Authority urgently
OL,15,Fadvises that the Thames is a very
OL,16,Fdifferent risk environment from a
OL,17,Fpark, pool or ordinary open-water
OL,18,Fsetting.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
