CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783694874
OL,3,CWater safety campaign warns of the
OL,4,Cdangers of the Thames
OL,6,FIt can look calm, familiar and
OL,7,Finviting from the bank, particularly
OL,8,Fduring hot weather but is a fast-
OL,9,Fmoving working river.
OL,11,FIn places, it can flow at up to 5mph -
OL,12,Ffaster than an Olympic swimmer - with
OL,13,Fcold water, strong currents, hidden
OL,14,Fhazards such as shopping trolleys and
OL,15,Fdebris, sudden depth changes, vessel
OL,16,Ftraffic and tidal conditions that can
OL,17,Foverwhelm even confident swimmers.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
