PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1783694874
OL,3,CWater safety campaign warns of the
OL,4,Cdangers of the Thames
OL,6,FNew Port of London research found that
OL,7,Fwhile young people often recognise the
OL,8,FThames can be dangerous, they do not
OL,9,Falways consider safety when they are
OL,10,Fwith their friends.
OL,12,FIt warns that in social summer
OL,13,Fsettings risks can escalate quickly
OL,14,Fand wants young people to be aware of
OL,15,Fthe risks involved when spending time
OL,16,Fby the water.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/4
